    <h1>Macro-Influencer</h1>
    <p class="description">A social media creator with <strong>100,000 to 1,000,000 followers</strong> who combines meaningful reach with niche authority. More affordable than celebrities, more far-reaching than micro-influencers.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
