          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">How are macro-influencers different from micro-influencers?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Micro-influencers have 10,000-100,000 followers with typically higher engagement rates (5-8%) at lower cost. Macro-influencers have 100,000-1,000,000 followers with 3-5% engagement but broader reach and more professional content quality.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Should you work with one macro-influencer or many micro-influencers?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Both approaches work. A single macro-influencer delivers concentrated reach and brand consistency. Multiple micro-influencers provide distributed recommendations across niche communities, often at lower total cost. Most brands use a mix: macro for awareness, micro for conversion.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">What engagement rate is good for a macro-influencer?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>3-5% engagement rate is the benchmark for macro-influencers. Below 2% on a large account often signals bought followers or audience fatigue. Above 5% on 100K+ followers indicates unusually strong community connection.</p></div></div>
          </div>
