            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Instagram and YouTube dominate macro-influencer marketing for B2C brands. LinkedIn macro-influencers are increasingly effective for B2B, particularly in marketing, SaaS, and professional services. TikTok macro-influencers are strong for Gen Z audiences.</p></div></div>
